"{\"uid\": \"en.tempo.co-read-1898900-paris-2024-facts-about-turkeys-viral-olympic-shooter-yusuf-dikec\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Translator  Ririe Ranggasari  Editor  Laila Afifa  August 2, 2024 | 11:44 am  TEMPO.CO,Jakarta-Turkish Olympic shooterYusuf Dikechas become a newfound Internet sensation for his cool and casual style.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laila_Bagge_Wahlgren\", \"score\": 0.9015589462394693, \"rank\": 0.10918981411745324, \"text\": \"Laila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laila_Bagge_Wahlgren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laila_Bagge_Wahlgren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The marksman wore standard glasses, a team T-shirt and had his hand casually in his pocket, his face rather expressionless, as photos circulating on social media suggested.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Netizens called him an ordinary man who just happened to be competing in theOlympics, and some even compared his style to that of a killer.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Indonesian netizens described him as a \\\"housing complex dad.\\\"\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.1509406917308876e-12, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Memes were quickly generated, some contrasting him with his Serbian opponent, Damir Mikec, who wore the official blinders over one eye, a lens over the other, and large ear protectors.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9998938586258942, \"rank\": 0.00010581949908336594, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Damir Mikec\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mikec and his partner Zorana Arunovi and Damir Mikec went on to win gold for the Serbian team.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Damir Mikec\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damir_Mikec\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9998938586258942, \"rank\": 0.00010581949908336594, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are some known facts about Yusuf Dikec, the Turkish Olympian who is -- at the moment -- an Internet sensation.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999008651, \"rank\": 5.810902238714658e-11, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}, {\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9610680697727413, \"rank\": 0.0403333689591827, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999991123332, \"rank\": 8.880308607992029e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 51-year-old Yusuf Dikec is no newcomer in the Olympics shooting range.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999008651, \"rank\": 5.810902238714658e-11, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's competed in every Summer Olympics since 2008.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris 2024, Dikec and Sevval Ilayda Tarhan won the silver medal in the 10-meter air pistol mixed team event last Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.643969062275356e-27, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Turkey's first medal in Olympic shooting.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999914674727048, \"rank\": 8.451540831863937e-06, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many shooters at the Olympic shooting range in Chateauroux, central France, choose to wear regulation visors, also called blinders, over one eye to reduce glare and get better focus.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999599464654323, \"rank\": 0.00040065829826789126, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He chose not to and shot with both eyes open.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While photos made it look like he wasn't protecting his ears during the competition, Dikec was actually wearing yellow earplugs during the finals.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the earplugs were not visible in the image that went viral.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dikec finished 13th in the singles and has now completed his run at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's looking ahead to the next games in 2028.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope to win a gold medal next time in Los Angeles,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 9.807123427099165e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bonus Trivia  Like Dikec, his partner Sevval Ilayda Tarhan also adopted a \\\"casual\\\" style of shooting with her hands in her pockets.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, 